Package: DROMA.Meta.visualization
Title: Publication-Quality Visualization for DROMA.Meta Workflow Results
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-16
Authors@R:
    person("Peng Yu", "Zhong", email = "yc47680@um.edu.mo", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Peng Yu Zhong [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Peng Yu Zhong <yc47680@um.edu.mo>
Description: Provides publication-ready visualization functions for the
    DROMA.Meta biomarker discovery pipeline. Generates volcano plots,
    effect-size heatmaps, preclinical-clinical concordance scatter plots,
    upset intersection diagrams, pipeline funnel summaries, and forest
    plots from the multi-stage meta-analysis workflow output.
